{"talk":{"id":62592,"name":"Huang Hung: How American and Chinese values shaped the coronavirus response","description":"To combat COVID-19, countries have enforced city-wide shutdowns, stay-at-home orders and mask mandates -- but the reaction (and adherence) to these rules has differed markedly in the East and West. In conversation with TED's head of curation Helen Walters, writer and publisher Huang Hung sheds light on how Chinese and American cultural values shaped their responses to the outbreak -- and provides perspective on why everyone needs to come together to end the pandemic. (Recorded April 16, 2020)","slug":"huang_hung_how_american_and_chinese_values_shaped_the_coronavirus_response","recorded_at":"2020-04-16 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-05-08 14:56:02","updated_at":"2020-12-26 21:27:01","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":644,"name":"TED2020 "},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/0a54afc0c196db0d2a69020063516150ac70a835_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/0a54afc0c196db0d2a69020063516150ac70a835_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/0a54afc0c196db0d2a69020063516150ac70a835_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/0a54afc0c196db0d2a69020063516150ac70a835_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/292ae8600081b464c25f887613141c96684624d6_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HuangHung_2020S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5807022,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HuangHung_2020S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":16054882,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HuangHung_2020S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44caf